item.title: CVE-2023-24834|2024-08-02T11:03:19.255Z -- wisdomgarden -- tronclass%20ilearn
item.description: WisdomGarden Tronclass has improper access control when uploading file. An authenticated remote attacker with general user privilege can exploit this vulnerability to access files belonging to other users by modifying the file ID within URL.
